data.description: This charming 3 bed 2 bath home is the perfect place to escape. Just up the Chetco River you are minutes from the beach, but out of the Fog Zone. Set on just over 1 acre of land, the home is surrounded by rolling hills and lush green forest. The back deck is the perfect spot to relax and enjoy the large back yard area. The home itself is spacious and well-appointed. The open floor plan connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. Natural light floods in through large windows, accentuating the bright and airy ambiance. The large main bedroom has an ensuite bathroom with an oversized tub and two sinks. The bedrooms offer ample space, closet storage, and large windows that provide natural light and pleasant views. Conveniently located in a peaceful rural area, this property offers the perfect balance between seclusion and accessibility. Enjoy the tranquility of country living while still being within a reasonable distance from essential amenities, schools, shopping centers, and just 4 minutes from the golf course. Don't miss this incredible opportunity to embrace the beauty of nature and experience the joys of rural living in this spacious home on a generous acre of land. Schedule your showing today and start envisioning your new chapter in this captivating retreat. SELLER IS MOTIVATED.
